snippet.title: Planet Coaster 2 - Game Overview | gamescom 2024
snippet.description: Take a peek at the new waterpark rides, platforms, color options, and scenery coming to Planet Coaster 2, releasing on PlayStation 5, Microsoft Windows, Xbox Series X and Series S this Fall.
